@to_reynolds squats are an exercise that can be through multiple ranges. In this case the range of the Squat is limited to work on the concept of “leg stiffness” to produce energy—basically the ability to absorb and recreate quickly some explosive action without needing excessive bend in the knees. Combining this in addition to full range squat jumps is a solid combo. Thanks for the feedback !
